<p>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</p>
<p>The housing process for <%= @college.name %> has entered the group formation phase. Please log in to <%= college_site_link(@college) %><%= @login_str %> to create or join a group.</p>
<% if @intent_locked %>
  <% if @user.intent != 'on-campus' %>
    Please note that intent declaration is now locked. If you wish to change your intent to on-campus, please contact <%= admin_mail_link(@college) %>
  <% end %>
<% else %>
  <p>
  You also can still declare or change your intent to live on- or off-campus for next year
  <% if @intent_deadline %>
    until <%= @intent_deadline %>.
  <% else %>.
  <% end %>
<% end %>
</p>
<p>Please e-mail <%= admin_mail_link(@college) %> if you have any questions.</p>
<p>Sincerely,<br /><%= @college.dean %></p>
